---
// Standalone route used to generate the static OG card image
// (rendered to 1200x630 PNG via headless screenshot, then saved to /public/og.png).
// Not linked from anywhere — the live site references /og.png directly.
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>CASA Ready — OG card</title>
    <style>
      * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      html, body { width: 1200px; height: 630px; overflow: hidden; }
      body {
        background: #0d1117;
        color: #e6edf3;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        padding: 70px 90px 60px;
        position: relative;
      }
      .grid-bg {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
          linear-gradient(rgba(48, 54, 61, 0.35) 1px, transparent 1px),
          linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(48, 54, 61, 0.35) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 48px 48px;
        mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at top right, transparent 30%, black 70%);
        -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at top right, transparent 30%, black 70%);
        opacity: 0.6;
      }
      .content { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
      .tag {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 18px;
        letter-spacing: 0.18em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #6e7681;
        margin-bottom: 36px;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 88px;
        line-height: 1.05;
        letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 36px;
        max-width: 1020px;
      }
      .accent { color: #58a6ff; }
      .lead {
        font-size: 28px;
        line-height: 1.45;
        color: #8b949e;
        max-width: 950px;
        margin-bottom: 48px;
      }
      .row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: flex-end;
      }
      .install {
        background: #161b22;
        border: 1px solid #30363d;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 18px 26px;
        font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace;
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #e6edf3;
      }
      .install .prompt { color: #6e7681; user-select: none; }
      .install .pkg { color: #58a6ff; }
      .meta {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #6e7681;
        text-align: right;
      }
      .meta .url {
        display: block;
        font-size: 26px;
        color: #e6edf3;
        font-weight: 500;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="grid-bg"></div>
    <div class="content">
      <p class="tag">Open source · MIT</p>
      <h1>Pass Google's <span class="accent">CASA Tier 2</span><br />without paying a consulting firm.</h1>
      <p class="lead">Open-source toolkit for the OWASP-ZAP + Supabase corner of CASA. YAML config, JSON-Schema-driven autocomplete, dogfooded against a real CASA submission.</p>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="install"><span class="prompt">$ </span>npm install -g <span class="pkg">casa-ready</span></div>
        <div class="meta"><span class="url">casaready.org</span>v0.3.1 · npm</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
